=Description=

"Pagoda Network is an assembly of Asian visionaries within the Ethereum community dedicated to enhance regional contributions and foster global collaboration. It serves as a decentralized platform for Asian builders and ecosystem leaders to integrate the diverse Asian cultures and philosophies, aiming to create impactful, long-term solutions that honor and sustain the rich heritage of the region. Through its activities, Pagoda strengthens connections within the community, encouraging a collective approach to building a sustainable and equitable future for Asia and beyond."


=Characteristics=

==The Protocol of Being==

... is a profound journey into the core of what it means to live harmoniously within ourselves and our communities. It is a guiding philosophy for the Pagoda community, focusing on mindfulness, resilience, and interconnectedness. 


* Interoperability

* Resilience

* Ecology

* Humanity


==Inter-Pagoda-Net==

"The Inter-Pagoda Network is designed to support the interconnectedness of the Pagoda community. This network stimulates the flow of information and resources for diverse community interactions, and a robust immune system that ensures the health and integrity of the network. The Inter-Pagoda Network is integral to maintaining the vitality and sustainability of the community, enabling it to thrive in a decentralized and collaborative environment."


==Pagoda Passport==

The Pagoda Passport is an innovative identity and credentialing system designed to enhance trust and facilitate the seamless flow of resources within the Pagoda community. Leveraging the ERC-6551 standard, the passport acts as a digital "backpack," enabling each member to carry their unique credentials and tokens across platforms. The passport system not only verifies participation and contributions through various proofs such as work, presence, and vibes but also fosters relational identities by acknowledging interpersonal connections formed within the community."


